{"tid":2089513,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"7.1大埔熱狗店被淋不明液體啊屌","createTime":"2020-07-01T16:57:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T17:15:57.000Z","uid":225524,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9825d6433c34a8d18d70e3cbf6a7d20d16f7241b","tid":2089513,"uid":225524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T16:57:49.000Z","msg":"事發晚上約十一時，大埔廣福道外賣熱狗店門外，一名男子突然從WA5136(另有中港牌)黑色車輛下車，手持一大桶不明液體淋向在埸多名途經的人民及等候外賣的人民和熱狗店，並且大聲高叫辱罵在場的人民，男子眼見人民舉起手機立即返回車輛，以超高速駛去，現場人民表示驚慌。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AdKc1A4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAdKc1A4.png&h=fd475a8b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/07/02/003934_81bd6cded8579004e9107c072dabd42c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F07%2F02%2F003934_81bd6cded8579004e9107c072dabd42c.png&h=c1527ec7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSorry 窮撚手機廢影唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />熱狗店店員同門口啲人都瀨撚晒野 dllm</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5pW3oRh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5pW3oRh.png&h=3b8ff906&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>现在是在給国家添乱是不是???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">最後一提 隻熱狗好撚好食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>可以嘅話平啲就更perfect池<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\nSorly for 1999"},{"pid":"0550cbf5827fbc8680565a59abd2f46655c49374","tid":2089513,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"